<% content_for :title, "Accessibility / Support | GTA FREE STEM" %>

<section class="single-page">
  <article class="content-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">About the project</p>
    <h1>Built for families, students, educators, and community groups</h1>
    <p>
      GTA FREE STEM is a public web platform for finding free and accessible STEM opportunities across Toronto,
      Peel, York, Durham, and Halton. Browsing is open to everyone, with plain-language descriptions, list-first
      discovery, map support, age and city filters, and focused tags for communities that often face barriers.
    </p>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div><strong>Frontend</strong><span>Rails views, Hotwire, responsive UI, light/dark-ready styling.</span></div>
      <div><strong>Backend</strong><span>Rails, PostgreSQL/PostGIS, admin review, public API.</span></div>
      <div><strong>Mobile</strong><span>Companion iOS app maintained in a separate public repo.</span></div>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
